  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 11d316df67cd8d542be369fdf08c7831, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::StageOneManager
  startDelay: 5
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 1659451626}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 589910226}
  dialogueLines:
  - Welcome Student to the First Stage! This stage is called the Truth Table Stage.
  - "To complete this stage:\\n\u2022 Find the correct blocks inside the houses\\n\u2022
    Place them in the Truth Table in the correct column and order"
  - "This Stage consists of three challenges with different difficulty levels:\\n\u2022
    Challenge 1 \u2013 Easy\\n\u2022 Challenge 2 \u2013 Normal\\n\u2022 Challenge
    3 \u2013 Hard"
  - Look at the upper-right corner. You have 3 Hearts. These are your chances. Mistakes
    will cost you one Heart.
  - "Mistakes include:\\n\u2022 Placing the wrong block\\n\u2022 Placing a block
    in the wrong column\\n\u2022 Placing blocks in the wrong order"
  - '"If you lose all Hearts, it''s Game Over. Complete all 3 challenges to open
    the portal. Good luck, and prove your logic skills!'
  gameplayInterface: {fileID: 1259893814}
  objectivesPanel: {fileID: 1196448535}
  rulesScrollPanel: {fileID: 142880751}
  truthTableRulesGroup: {fileID: 2071171740}
  playerInput: {fileID: 540703228072888002}
